**EndpointPulseMap**  
**Description:**  
Tracks real-time performance of multiple APIs and maps out their latency pulses and availability.

```markdown
# EndpointPulseMap - Live API Pulse Monitor

EndpointPulseMap provides a timeline of uptime and latency signals across distributed services.

## Features
- Visual latency pulse map  
- Failure burst tracking  
- CSV and JSON output

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/EndpointPulseMap.git
cd EndpointPulseMap
python monitor.py
